0.text: Yesterday was a very enjoyable day. Our family was at home as it was a holiday. I got up at half past six in the morning. We had our breakfast together. Then my sister and I cleaned our room. We helped father to weed the garden too. Mother prepared a delicious meal and we enjoyed it. After lunch we all watched a family movie. It was an interesting adventure story. In the evening father played badminton with us. Mother sat outside and watched us play. After that, I did my homework. My sister helped me with it. Then we all had dinner and went to bed.
